    <h3 itemprop="headline">Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte urges support for Ukraine, EU and NATO in his farewell speech</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      THE HAGUE, Netherlands (AP) — Long-serving Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte urged his country to support Ukraine and international cooperation in his final address to his compatriots Sunday, as an inward-looking new government is set to take over the Netherlands in two days.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/07/01/dutch-prime-minister-mark-rutte-urged-support-for-ukraine-eu-and-nato-in-his-farewell-speech/"  >(MOLLY QUELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
