    <h3 itemprop="headline">Pope Francis Decrees Vatican Radio Territory in Northern Rome to be Repurposed into Solar Farm</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Pope Francis has decreed that a territory in northern Rome, previously criticized for emitting electromagnetic waves from Vatican Radio towers, will now house a field of solar panels to power Vatican City, aligning with the Vatican's pledge at the UN
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/a-vatican-radio-territory-in-north-rome-once-blamed-for-electro-smog-will-become-a-solar-farm/"  >(NICOLE WINFIELD, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
