    <h3 itemprop="headline">Klay Thompson enters free agency, expected to leave Warriors: reports</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      (KRON) — The Golden State Warriors are likely losing a franchise legend. Klay Thompson has entered free agency and is expected to leave the Warriors, according to multiple reports from The Athletic's Shams Charania and ESPN's Adrian Wojnarowski.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/30/klay-thompson-enters-free-agency-expected-to-leave-warriors-reports/"  >(Aaron Tolentino, KRON4)</a>
