    <h3 itemprop="headline">With England survival at stake, Jude Bellingham creates one of the great moments of Euro 2024</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      England has advanced to the quarterfinals of the European Championship after Jude Bellingham scored a stunning overhead kick in the fifth minute of stoppage time to spark a 2-1 comeback win after extra time against Slovakia.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/30/bellingham-wonder-goal-sends-england-vs-slovakia-to-extra-time-after-1-1-draw/"  >(James Robson, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
