    <h3 itemprop="headline">Wimbledon is set to start with Carlos Alcaraz, Emma Raducanu and Coco Gauff on the schedule</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WIMBLEDON, England (AP) — The 2024 edition of Wimbledon is scheduled to start on Monday, with defending champion Carlos Alcaraz and past Grand Slam title winners Coco Gauff and Emma Raducanu all set to play in matches at Centre Court.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/07/01/wimbledon-is-set-to-start-with-carlos-alcaraz-emma-raducanu-and-coco-gauff-on-the-schedule/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
