           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Like father, like son: Lakers select Bronny James in NBA Draft</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Los Angeles Lakers have selected Bronny James with the 55th overall pick in the 2024 NBA Draft, raising the likelihood that the former USC Trojan will take the court with his father, future Hall-of-Famer LeBron James. Bronny, aka LeBron James Jr.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/like-father-like-son-lakers-select-bronny-james-in-nba-draft/"  >(Travis Schlepp, KTLA 5)</a>
