  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/29/biden-is-making-appeals-to-donors-as-concerns-persist-over-his-presidential-debate-performance.webp" alt="Biden makes appeals to donors as concerns persist over his presidential debate performance"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden makes appeals to donors as concerns persist over his presidential debate performance</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Joe Biden looked to recapture his mojo and reassured donors that he’s fully up to the challenge of beating Donald Trump.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/29/biden-is-making-appeals-to-donors-as-concerns-persist-over-his-presidential-debate-performance/"  >(Josh Boak And Steve Peoples, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
