           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How replacing Biden as Democratic nominee would actually work</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Replacing President Biden as the Democratic nominee would be highly complicated, and likely impossible, unless the president voluntarily decided to back out on his own.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/29/how-replacing-biden-as-democratic-nominee-would-actually-work/"  >(Jared Gans, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
