           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden's difficult debate puts spotlight on Harris</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden’s lackluster debate performance has thrust Vice President Harris into the spotlight. After Biden struggled against former President Trump, Harris hit the airwaves to defend her running mate’s record and ability to handle the job.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/30/bidens-difficult-debate-puts-spotlight-on-harris/"  >(Brett Samuels, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
