    <h3 itemprop="headline">How the CNN mute button will work at tonight's Biden-Trump debate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The mute button is intended to help viewers understand the candidates, but it also carries risks for CNN.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/27/how-the-cnn-mute-button-will-work-at-tonights-biden-trump-debate/"  >(Dominick Mastrangelo, WGN 9)</a>
