           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Voting begins in NY primary election</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (PIX11) – The polls are officially open Tuesday for the primary election in New York. Polls in the state are open from 6 a.m. to 9 p.m.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/25/voting-begins-in-ny-primary-election/"  >(Erin Pflaumer, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
